strongs_def: an enclitic particle of indefiniteness; yet, even; used only in the comparative. See G3369 (-πω), G3380 (-πω), G3764 (-πω), G3768 (-πω), G4455 (-πω).
derivation: another form of the base of G4458 (-πω);
outline:
1. yet, even
  2. used only in compound with words 3369, 3380, 3764, 3768, 4455
